The paper describes the deployment of a heterogeneous many-core platform for experiments on custom interconnects and management of fault and critical events, applied to many-process applications. This involves topics related to computer architecture (cs.AR), distributed computing (cs.DC), embedded systems (cs.ET), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and systems and control (cs.SY).
